title: No Man's Sky Update 5 Experimental
description:
#################
#### WARNING ####
#################

If your game works without the patch, YOU DO NOT NEED IT!
This is mainly a patch for AMD processors (Phenom, Athlon) crashes.



####################
#### PATCH INFO ####
####################

This patch consists of No Man's Sky Experimental 5 (by machine4578) and all others as well.
So, you do not need patches 1, 2, 3, 4 - this one includes them.

Setup instructions:
1) Extract everything from .zip to your No Man's Sky game folder, overwrite everything;
2) Change PlayerName in file "BinariesALI213.ini"
